title: Celebrity Gossip- One Direction Origin Story
description: Joseph Quinn from Stranger Things did his first Late Night TV interview last night… but he almost didn’t make it into the country in time. And remember how Liam Payne claimed that Simon Cowell built One Direction around him? Well there is some unseen footage from The X Factor UK that shows Liam is, at best, exaggerating the truth. We’ll let you hear how the band was formed next.
